{"tid":589431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啟晴班on9蝗真係飲得鉛水多，餐餐都投建帝派","createTime":"2018-03-12T00:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T05:20:28.000Z","uid":51271,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"234148a7e3a35383d6d8bcfeac7f2106c4660b03","tid":589431,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:52:21.000Z","msg":"呢班人真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af57adef7265c102f44d63d2fa25b4c26595495","tid":589431,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:53:28.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾"},{"pid":"43e83c924b7622196447ca64cc171203f123f3b5","tid":589431,"uid":33651,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:54:21.000Z","msg":"抵班弱智繼續飲"},{"pid":"e813ff524fe2cd018b4249f291d41e30b91578be","tid":589431,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:11:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n「姚松炎今次做選舉工程，同我哋傳統政黨，真係好唔同，我哋唔係好慣，尤其係打開地面戰嗰班，其實一直覺得佢危。<br />\n<br />\n我哋擺街站、洗樓、去屋邨，佢哋認為唔使做好多呢啲，覺得做好網上，網上反應熱烈，就好有信心。<br />\n<br />\n即使佢哋助選團，或者幫忙嘅團體開（街）站，但好似用錯力，星期五、六下晝，喺佐敦開站，我哋一般唔會咁做，因為嗰啲係街客，去行街，唔係選民；即使開喺住宅區，有啲朝早9點後先至開，嗰啲時間，人人返晒工，開站都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎團隊去土瓜灣少數族裔拉票，好奇怪，或者踩單車，我哋好多人睇到，暈低咁滯。或者係我哋太傳統，唔慣咁做。<br />\n<br />\n不過泛民好多大佬，就好buy佢呢套，所以一直覺得九西呢個位好易贏，無咩危機感，其實我地做開地區嘅，睇佢唔係咁穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋呢種選舉工程，喺比例代表制，效果可能會比較好，今次補選只係選一個位，未必可以咁打選戰。今次投票率咁低，有好多原因，如果唔諗點樣做，下次補選，我擔心唔容易贏。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=65e18a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e96c93c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3b3284c0fb9ce2d4e408f38e2e56739e2555c46","tid":589431,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/084237_74e818d7da05ecbe8e2e0a7ea708fdf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F084237_74e818d7da05ecbe8e2e0a7ea708fdf9.png&h=6c9baf49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多撚謝販民班大愛支（尤其民主党工党同社民狗！）囉！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啟德一早都知係港共專登設計既市區票倉膽！！！！</span></span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n「姚松炎今次做選舉工程，同我哋傳統政黨，真係好唔同，我哋唔係好慣，尤其係打開地面戰嗰班，其實一直覺得佢危。<br />\n<br />\n我哋擺街站、洗樓、去屋邨，佢哋認為唔使做好多呢啲，覺得做好網上，網上反應熱烈，就好有信心。<br />\n<br />\n即使佢哋助選團，或者幫忙嘅團體開（街）站，但好似用錯力，星期五、六下晝，喺佐敦開站，我哋一般唔會咁做，因為嗰啲係街客，去行街，唔係選民；即使開喺住宅區，有啲朝早9點後先至開，嗰啲時間，人人返晒工，開站都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎團隊去土瓜灣少數族裔拉票，好奇怪，或者踩單車，我哋好多人睇到，暈低咁滯。或者係我哋太傳統，唔慣咁做。<br />\n<br />\n不過泛民好多大佬，就好buy佢呢套，所以一直覺得九西呢個位好易贏，無咩危機感，其實我地做開地區嘅，睇佢唔係咁穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋呢種選舉工程，喺比例代表制，效果可能會比較好，今次補選只係選一個位，未必可以咁打選戰。今次投票率咁低，有好多原因，如果唔諗點樣做，下次補選，我擔心唔容易贏。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=65e18a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e96c93c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cd6e5f09e509b5b703de3506c427f7ed35f0676","tid":589431,"uid":51127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:17:43.000Z","msg":"人地民賤聯有咁多彈藥招呼街坊，其他人點同佢玩，叫個班人同你班港豬講理想，真係hi大左。"},{"pid":"2d6018fac3ca58af83c8bab18e9c8c7636152765","tid":589431,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:18:51.000Z","msg":"泛民啟德冇做過野?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583392274ec9135a140b869003f0a59a77dc0309","tid":589431,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:21:44.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n條友真係冇乜宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋睇見本簿好多後生都冇去投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：九西投咗俾佢"},{"pid":"64de02cea6954d0b306f696b90bad557cf9f49b5","tid":589431,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d6018fac3ca58af83c8bab18e9c8c7636152765","tid":589431,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:18:51.000Z","msg":"泛民啟德冇做過野?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"應該話周圍都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a628